<div class="pub mb-5">
  <div class="pub-image"><img src="/assets/img/publications/featured.webp" class="thumb rounded" alt="Electrochemical Hydrogen Isotope Exchange of Amines Controlled by Alternating Current Frequency"></div>
  <div class="pub-body">
    <div class="pub-badge-wrap"><span class="pub-badge">Faraday Discuss.</span></div>
    <div class="pub-title fw-semibold h5 mb-0"><a class="pub-title-link" href="/publications/articles/behera-gunasekera-2023/">Electrochemical Hydrogen Isotope Exchange of Amines Controlled by Alternating Current Frequency</a></div>
