    <div class="pub-title fw-semibold h5 mb-0"><a class="pub-title-link" href="/publications/articles/aryal-frimpong-liu-2022/">Comparative Study of Covalent and van Der Waals CdS Quantum Dot Assemblies from Many-Body Perturbation Theory</a></div>
    <div class="text-muted small mt-1">Sandip Aryal, Joseph Frimpong, Zhen-Fei Liu</div>
    <div class="text-muted small">J. Phys. Chem. Lett., 13(43): 10153-10161</div>
    <div class="pub-actions">

      <button class="btn btn-sm btn-light" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#abs-a0a39f92" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="abs-a0a39f92">ABSTRACT</button>
