    <div class="pub-title fw-semibold h5 mb-0"><a class="pub-title-link" href="/publications/articles/frimpong-liu-2021/">Quasiparticle Electronic Structure of Two-Dimensional Heterotriangulene-Based Covalent Organic Frameworks Adsorbed on Au(111)</a></div>
